./docs/implementation.md:83:OIDC/JWKS failures are classified at the verifier boundary:
./docs/implementation.md:85:- Provider failure: network failures, timeouts, non-200 JWKS responses, malformed JWKS JSON, malformed JWKS shape, and ambiguous JWKS key matches. In these cases cyspbot could not obtain a usable trusted key set, so `/token` returns `503 {"error":"temporarily_unavailable"}`.
